	(1835,815,'prospectnow_portal_real_estate_content','Looking for more listings? <strong>ProspectNow</strong> helps you identify properties that are most likely to be listed for sale in the next 12 months before your competition does. Why waste time and energy to marketing to property owners that will never sell? ProspectNow’s predictive algorithm looks at hundreds of data points each week on properties that are actually selling…then, we apply the characteristics of properties that just sold to properties that have yet to sell.\r\n\r\nWhat does this mean for you? Click on the button below to find out how much additional commissions you might be able to earn using <strong>ProspectNow</strong>.'),
	(1836,815,'_prospectnow_portal_real_estate_content','field_58c0dea17b6a0'),
	(1837,815,'prospectnow_portal_lenders_content','Looking to close more loans? <strong>ProspectNow</strong> helps you identify properties that are most likely refinance or obtain a loan in the next 12 months before your competition does. Why waste time and energy to marketing to property owners that will get a loan? ProspectNow’s patent pending predictive algorithm looks at hundreds of data points each week on properties that are actually refinancing…then, we apply the characteristics of properties that just refinanced to properties that have yet to refinance.\r\n\r\nWhat does this mean for you? Click on the button below to find out how much loan revenue you might be able to earn using <strong>ProspectNow</strong>.'),
