	(7626,1606,'_prospectnow_ip_marketing_page_hero_title','field_58d8f22448a17'),
	(7627,1606,'prospectnow_ip_marketing_page_hero_content','Sit back, relax, and let the leads flow in! ProspectNow can manage an entire digital ad campaign directly to the property owners you want to target. Combining ProspectNow?s predictive analytics with digital ad deliver directly to the property owners results in tremendously targeted campaigns with very high rates of success.'),
