	(7630,1606,'_prospectnow_ip_marketing_stop_robots_title','field_58d8f269ace58'),
	(7631,1606,'prospectnow_ip_marketing_stop_robots_content','It sounds hard to believe but, more than half of internet ads are actually never seen by a human being. Can you believe that? Bots and crawlers scour the internet and are triggering ads to be displayed that will never reach their intended audience. This costs advertisers billions of dollars in wasted ad spend.'),
