	(50,1,'2014-12-08 19:49:43','2014-12-08 19:49:43','<div class=\"align-center\">\r\n<div class=\"text-center\" style=\"padding-left: 20px; padding-right: 20px;\">\r\n<h1 class=\"entry-title\">The Most Effective Prospecting System in Commercial Real Estate</h1>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row demo-entry\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-10 col-md-offset-1\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-12 col-md-6\">\r\n<h1>All of Your Property and Tenant Data in One Place</h1>\r\nProspectNow combines phone numbers for the building owners, property, financial data, tenants information and all the tools you need to manage your prospecting efforts.  Find sellers and list properties before your competition does.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-12 col-md-6 \"><a class=\"testimonialDemo\" onclick=\"loadYoutube(\'4R-wFygPaiw\');return false;\" href=\"#\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-target=\"#myModal\"> </a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row demo-entry\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-10 col-md-offset-1\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-12 col-md-6 hidden-xs\"><a class=\"testimonialDemo\" onclick=\"loadYoutube(\'aAh9Vn9IJSY\');return false;\" href=\"#\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-target=\"#myModal\"> </a></div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-12 col-md-6\">\r\n<h1>Search Commercial & Residential Owners</h1>\r\nFilter by building size, sale price, loan amount, number of properties owned and much more. You can also search for out of state residential & commercial building owners, or number of properties that an owner owns. ProspectNow enables you to make fewer cold calls and focus on working with clients that actually want to do business.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-12 col-md-6 hidden-lg\"><a class=\"testimonialDemo\" onclick=\"loadYoutube(\'aAh9Vn9IJSY\');return false;\" href=\"#\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-target=\"#myModal\"> </a></div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row demo-entry\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-10 col-md-offset-1\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-12 col-md-6\">\r\n<h1>Commercial Tenant Search</h1>\r\nIf you are searching for tenants looking for space, you can filter by number of employees, revenue, location and even if the tenant owns the property or leases it.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-12 col-md-6 \"><a class=\"testimonialDemo\" onclick=\"loadYoutube(\'_gCtEVUtsoE\');return false;\" href=\"#\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-target=\"#myModal\"> </a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row demo-entry\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-10 col-md-offset-1\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-12 col-md-6 hidden-xs\"><a class=\"testimonialDemo\" onclick=\"loadYoutube(\'hflCiUutzg0\');return false;\" href=\"#\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-target=\"#myModal\"> </a></div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-12 col-md-6\">\r\n<h1>Send Mail</h1>\r\nSend post mail to residential & commercial building owners and tenants with the push of a button. That\'s right, you can use ProspectNow to do mailing campaigns to property and company owners and you can do it all from the comfort of your desktop or tablet. We actually stuff the envelopes, apply the postage, and mail it for you. If you have an active subscription, you can simply purchase \"Mail Credits\" and use them as you require.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-12 col-md-6 hidden-lg\"><a class=\"testimonialDemo\" onclick=\"loadYoutube(\'hflCiUutzg0\');return false;\" href=\"#\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-target=\"#myModal\"> </a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row demo-entry\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-10 col-md-offset-1\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-12 col-md-6\">\r\n<h1>Contact Management</h1>\r\nSo you have all your data and marketing tools, but what about managing your prospecting efforts. With ProspectNow, you can track your notes, pipeline, and activity all within the system. If you are a real estate broker, lender, or banker...all of your deals will in visible and organized within ProspectNow.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-12 col-md-6 \"><a class=\"testimonialDemo\" onclick=\"loadYoutube(\'HuecYqSkuDo\');return false;\" href=\"#\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-target=\"#myModal\"> </a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row demo-entry\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-10 col-md-offset-1\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-12 col-md-6 hidden-xs\"><a class=\"testimonialDemo\" onclick=\"loadYoutube(\'HL3Fuf-n848\');return false;\" href=\"#\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-target=\"#myModal\"> </a></div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-12 col-md-6\">\r\n<h1>Activity Tracking</h1>\r\nIf you manage a team of users, we provide you everything you need to monitor and team activity.  Track your team\'s deals from initial contact to close.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row demo-entry\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-10 col-md-offset-1\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-12 col-md-6\">\r\n<h1>Mobile App Demo</h1>\r\nProperty information wherever you are. If you are driving by a property and see it would be a great fit for a client, simply access the info on ProspectNow on your phone. Enter a note and even call the owner while in the field.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-12 col-md-6\"><a class=\"testimonialDemo\" onclick=\"loadYoutube(\'sMbvYQ3DCcc\');return false;\" href=\"#\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-target=\"#myModal\"> </a></div>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"row demo-entry\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-10 col-md-offset-1\">\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-12 col-md-6 hidden-xs\"><a class=\"testimonialDemo\" onclick=\"loadYoutube(\'qgXcirU-Gcg\');return false;\" href=\"#\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-target=\"#myModal\"> </a></div>\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-12 col-md-6\">\r\n<h1>Nationwide Search Capability</h1>\r\nUse ProspectNow to quickly search across multiple counties, states, or even the whole United States with just a few simple clicks.\r\n\r\n