d we recommend that users and subscribers check this site frequently. However, any changes of a material nature in the privacy policy will be communicated to you here, by notice on our homepage, and/or by e-mail.</p>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n','Terms of Use','','inherit','closed','closed','','451-revision-v1','','','2014-04-14 12:26:48','2014-04-14 12:26:48','',451,'http://wordpress.list-trac.com//451-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
