	(545,1,'2014-07-11 23:51:38','2014-07-11 23:51:38','<h1 class=\"entry-title\">Products - Find Commercial & Apartment Building Owners</h1>\r\n<div class=\"row\">\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n<h2>ProspectNow is the ultimate tool for closing more real estate deals and finding buyers, sellers, or borrowers.  ProspectNow has an online database of 100 million commercial and residential building owners that includes phone numbers, mailing addresses and building details.</h2>\r\n<a class=\"btn og\" href=\"search-commercial-real-estate\">Search Database</a>\r\n<h2>Property Database</h2>\r\nSearch more than 100 million commercial & residential properties nationwide by location, size, property type, building details, LTV and more. Access owner mailing addresses and telephone numbers instantly. Use ProspectNow to add email addresses for your existing customers and relationships. Utilize the latest direct mailing tools to create targeted marketing campaigns and accumulate clients.\r\n\r\n<h2>Commercial Tenant Database</h2>\r\nSearch more than 30 million commercial tenants and companies nationwide. The ProspectNow tenant database can be used to target tenants and decision makers to help you close more deals. The tenant data includes data such as the annual sales, number of employees, key contacts, year founded, and the amount of space leased.\r\n\r\n<h2>Contact Management and Call Tracking</h2>\r\nProspectNow allows you to track the progress and sales activity of not just yourself, but your entire team of sales agents. The data and software are completely integrated, so your sales team can obtain thousands of leads while you are provided with the metrics necessary to measure your business success. The best part about the ProspectNow CRM tool is that you can integrate it however you like. You can have a team approach where all sales people see the same leads, or an individual approach where each salesperson only sees his or her own leads. ProspectNow is the only system on the market to date that provides leads, data feeds and contact management tools all in a single application. Just turn it on and start prospecting.\r\n\r\n<h2>Data File Downloads</h2>\r\nIf you already have a CRM you like to use, ProspectNow also offers a data export feature that allows you to download the data to Excel so you can load it into your CRM. For more information, Contact Us or call 888-956-9998.\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\r\n<div class=\"peach_background\">\r\n<b>Advanced Search Results</b>\r\n<img src=\"http://adarsh.prospectnow.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/products-search-results.jpg\" alt=\"products-search-results\" style=\"width:100%;max-width:398px;\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-43\" />\r\n\r\n<b>Property Details</b>\r\n<img src=\"http://adarsh.prospectnow.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/products-property-details.jpg\" alt=\"products-property-details\" style=\"width:100%;max-width:399px;\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-44\" />\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n</div>','Products - Find Commercial and Apartment Building Owners','','inherit','closed','closed','','13-revision-v1','','','2014-07-11 23:51:38','2014-07-11 23:51:38','',13,'http://wordpress.list-trac.com//13-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(549,1,'2014-07-14 20:56:58','2014-07-14 20:56:58','<h1 class=\"entry-title\">About Us- The Prospecting Real Estate Database Redefined</h1>\nProspectNow has the most complete residential & commercial real estate prospecting database on the market. The ProspectNow property database boasts more than 100 million properties (residential, commercial, and industrial) nationwide that can be searched by a property\'s location, size, type and more. Subscribers can view building details and access owner mailing addresses and telephone numbers instantly. Users can also search and view the details on more than 30 million businesses and tenants. Finally, ProspectNow provides its subscribers with state-of-the-art CRM software and mailing tools that can enhance their sales approach.\n<div class=\"peach_background\">\n<h3><strong>ProspectNow Team</strong></h3>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-md-1 text-center\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-111\" style=\"margin: 0 10px 10px 0;\" alt=\"stevewayne\" src=\"http://adarsh.prospectnow.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/stevewayne.png\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></div>\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 col-md-11\">\n<h5><strong>Steven Wayne, Founder &amp; CEO <a href=\"http://www.linkedin.com/in/stevenwayne\"><img class=\"alignnone\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.prospectnow.com/images/linkedin_icon_small.gif\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></a> <a href=\"http://twitter.com/SteveWayne\"><img class=\"alignnone\" alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.prospectnow.com/images/twitter_icon_small.gif\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></a></strong></h5>\nPrior to launching ProspectNow, Wayne successfully sold retail shopping centers in Northern California at Marcus &amp; Millichap. Having millions of dollars in transaction experience, Wayne understood the need in the commercial real estate industry for an all-in-one database. Using his 10 years of expertise within the software industry, and relying upon the knowledge he gained from founding three other successful technology companies,Wayne set out to make the search process easier for commercial agents.. Wayne holds a Bachelor of Science in mechanical engineering from the University of Arizona. He resides in Los Altos, CA with his wife and two sons.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n&nbsp;\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-md-1 col-xs-12  text-center\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-113\" style=\"margin: 0 10px 10px 0;\" alt=\"dennis\" src=\"http://adarsh.prospectnow.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/01/dennis.jpg\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" /></div>\n<div class=\"col-md-11 col-xs-12\">\n<h5><strong>Dennis DeAndre, Investor</strong></h5>\nDeAndre has made a successful career acquiring and investing in privately-held companies. He most famously founded LoopNet.com (NASDAQ: LOOP) in 1995, and served as the company\'s chairman and CEO while it evolved into the Internet\'s largest commercial real estate exchange. DeAndre also owned and operated BizBuySell.com and BizQuest.com, the two of the Internet\'s largest business-for-sale marketplaces, as well as a number of other private companies. He graduated from the School of Business at UC Berkeley, with an emphases in real estate and finance.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>','About Us - The Commercial Real Estate Database Redefined','','inherit','closed','closed','','96-autosave-v1','','','2014-07-14 20:56:58','2014-07-14 20:56:58','',96,'http://wordpress.list-trac.com//96-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
