	(1152,4,'2017-03-23 08:29:30','2017-03-23 08:29:30','<h1>Find property sellers. Get more listings.</h1>\n\n<h2>Whether you want to contact expired, withdrawn, or FSBO listings, find phone numbers for owners of investment portfolios, or simply reach out to more potential sellers, ProspectNow is the ultimate tool for closing more real estate deals and finding buyers, sellers, or borrowers. ProspectNow has an online database of 100 million residential building owners that includes phone numbers, mailing addresses and property details.</h2>\n\n<center><a class=\"btn og\" href=\"search-residential-real-estate\">Try It Free</a></center>\n\n<h2>Property Database</h2>\n\nSearch more than 100 million residential properties nationwide by location, size, property type, building details, LTV and more. Access owner mailing addresses and telephone numbers instantly. Use ProspectNow to add email addresses for your existing customers and relationships. Utilize the latest direct mailing tools to create targeted marketing campaigns and accumulate clients.\n\n<h2>Data Driven Approach</h2>\n\nUse ProspectNow\'s enhanced targeting features to pinpoint high value prospects, such as:\n\n<ul style=\"padding-left:10px;\">\n	<li>Empty nesters that want to downsize</li>\n	<li>Expired, withdrawn and FSBO listings</li>\n	<li>Owners of 16 million rental properties</li>\n	<li>Investment property owners that are hidden behind LLCs, Corporations and Trusts</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2>Contact Management and Call Tracking</h2>\n\nProspectNow allows you to track the progress and sales activity of not just yourself, but your entire team of sales agents. The data and software are completely integrated, so your sales team can obtain thousands of leads while you are provided with the metrics necessary to measure your business success. The best part about the ProspectNow CRM tool is that you can integrate it however you like. You can have a team approach where all sales people see the same leads, or an individual 